      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi Magnus,</p>\n<p>I’m sure you’re already aware you can be reminded at a particular date using this recipe:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/3/233c255cde0233f1bae72a0677e321b2e6cf3e24.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/3/233c255cde0233f1bae72a0677e321b2e6cf3e24.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"332\" height=\"113\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">443×151 4.73 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>If you want to be reminded before or after, there are more options for date calculation available out of the box these days. You can configure something like this in the automation centre:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/0/0082c61a1daccccc5ef406dc81f3c217770eed5b.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/0/0082c61a1daccccc5ef406dc81f3c217770eed5b_2_517x258.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"517\" height=\"258\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1143×572 33 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>You can combine this with the date-arrives notification recipe from before to get reminded before or after a date.</p>\n<p>If you want to be reminder a certain number of minutes or hours before a date, you can use this automation from the <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000944/calendar-plus?utm_source=community&amp;utm_content=\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Automato</a> app:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/1/a11b373323d1e397d70f688e5058ad0807aef1d6.png\" title=\"10 minutes before Meeting start arrives Then notify Person\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/1/a11b373323d1e397d70f688e5058ad0807aef1d6.png\" alt=\"10 minutes before Meeting start arrives Then notify Person\" width=\"690\" height=\"200\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">10 minutes before Meeting start arrives Then notify Person</span><span class=\"informations\">754×219 14.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>–<br />\n<a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000944/calendar-plus?utm_source=community&amp;utm_content=\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/8/483886dd210fbd60b74ef4714cb139323cc802b8.png\" alt=\"Install Automato\" width=\"400\" height=\"56\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000944/calendar-plus?utm_source=community&amp;utm_content=\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Automato on monday marketplace</strong></a> | <a href=\"https://automagical.work/automato/automations?utm_source=community&amp;utm_content=\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Complete automation reference</a> | <a href=\"https://automagical.work/automato/pricing?utm_source=community&amp;utm_content=\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Pricing</a></p>"
